

// file should exetenction FileName.conf 
// location Where to find files for this path 

    
//     allow methods 
//     listing off on 
// server{
//         Purpose: defines one server instance with IP, port, error pages, and location blocks.

//         Mandatory attributes:

//         listen → IP and port

//         client_max_body_size → max request size

//         At least one location block

//         Optional attributes:

//         server_name

//         error_page (other than default)

//         Any custom global directives

//         locatoin {
            
//             Purpose: define rules for a specific URL path.

//             Mandatory attributes inside a location:

//             root

//             index

//             allow_methods

//             autoindex

//             Optional attributes:

//             cgi_extension + cgi_path

//             upload_store

//             return <code> <url>; for redirection
//             diractives{
//                 Examples:
//                 root /var/www/html;

//                 index index.html;

//                 allow_methods GET POST;

//                 autoindex on;

//                 cgi_extension .php;

//                 cgi_path /usr/bin/php-cgi;

//                 upload_store /var/www/uploads;

//                 error_page 404 /errors/404.html;

//                 client_max_body_size 2000000;
//             }

//         }
    
//     }

//     RULES{
     
    
//     Every directive ends with ;

//     Every block { ... } is properly closed

//     Each server must have at least one location

//     Each location must define mandatory attributes

//     Only recognized directives are allowed

//     Nested blocks must follow proper order (server → location)
//}

    
+------------------+
|  servers (vector)|
+------------------+
        |
        |  contains multiple Server objects
        v
   +------------------------+
   |       Server           |
   +------------------------+
   | listen_ip              |
   | listen_port            |
   | max_body_size          |
   | locations (vector)     |  --> multiple Location objects
   +------------------------+
               |
               v
        +------------------+
        |     Location     |
        +------------------+
        | path             |
        | directives (vector) | --> multiple Directive objects
        +------------------+
                  |
                  v
           +----------------+
           |   Directive    |
           +----------------+
           | name           |  (e.g., "root", "index")
           | args (vector)  |  (e.g., ["index.html"], ["GET","POST"])
           +----------------+

toknizer is good to parsing like {} and path location 
port var should be like IP:PORT 
